desc: GreenCrate offers organic produce delivery in the Los Angeles area. Our greenhouse produce is fully organic, non-GMO, and absolutely delicious. Get your bulk produce and save money on the food you need to be healthy for 2022.

layout.text: Fresh organic produce grown in your neighborhood, delivered by authentic 1928 Farm Trucks.If you love feeling good, saving money, and really cool vintage cars, welcome my friend.We are here to provide healthy produce to all those who need it, and make the world a little greener one crate at a time.
